              "content": "# PRD: OKX Intent Swap SDK\n\n\u003e Product Requirements Document — What are we building?\n\n**Related**: [BRD](./brd.md) | [Spec](./spec.md) | [Plan](./plan.md)\n\n## 1. Overview\n\n- **Product**: OKX Intent Swap SDK (`@okx-intent-swap/sdk-*`)\n- **Description**: TypeScript SDK，将 Solver API `/solve` 的请求/响应数据转化为可直接提交到 `Settlement.settle()` 合约的 calldata，并提供反向解码与 round-trip 验证能力\n- **Target Users**: 外部 Solver 开发团队（TypeScript/JavaScript 技术栈）\n- **Personas**:\n  - **Solver Developer**: 需要快速构建并提交 settlement calldata\n  - **Protocol Auditor**: 需要解码和验证链上 calldata 的正确性\n  - **Integration Engineer**: 负责将 SDK 集成到 Solver 基础设施中\n\n## 2. Core Concepts\n\n### 2.1 Domain Model\n\n```\nSettlement Protocol\n  ├── Auction (auctionId → settleId)\n  │     └── has many: Order (user intent)\n  ├── Solution (solver's proposed execution)\n  │     ├── ClearingPrices (per token)\n  │     ├── has many: ExecutedOrder (execution result)\n  │     └── SurplusFeeInfo (protocol fee)\n  └── Settlement Transaction\n        ├── Calldata (ABI-encoded settle() params)\n        ├── Tokens[] (deduplicated address list)\n        ├── Trades[] (on-chain order representation)\n        └── Interactions[3] (pre-swap, swap, post-swap)\n```\n\n### 2.2 Key Concepts\n\n| Concept | Definition | Key Attributes |\n|---------|-----------|---------------|\n| **SolveRequest** | Solver API 请求体，包含待结算订单 | auctionId, orders[] |\n| **SolveResponse** | Solver API 响应体，包含解决方案 | solutions[].clearingPrices, orders[], surplusFeeInfo |\n| **Trade** | 链上订单表示，引用 token 索引而非地址 | fromTokenAddressIndex, toTokenAddressIndex, executedAmount, flags(packed) |\n| **CommissionInfo** | 佣金配置，flag 字段为打包的位掩码 | feePercent(1e9), referrerWalletAddress, flag(direction\\|toB\\|label) |\n| **Interaction** | 结算过程中的链上调用 | target, value, callData |\n| **ClearingPrice** | 每个 token 的结算价格 | API: decimal string → on-chain: uint256 bigint |\n\n### 2.3 Two Type Systems\n\n```\nAPI Wire Format (decimal strings)     On-Chain Format (bigint + packed flags)\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━         ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\nSolveRequest                    →     settle() params\n  .auctionId: string            →       settleId: bigint\n  .orders[].fromTokenAmount: string →   Trade.fromTokenAmount: bigint\n  .orders[].commissionInfos[]   →       Trade.commissionInfos[].flag: bigint (packed)\n\nApiCommissionInfo               →     CommissionInfo\n  .feeDirection: boolean        →       flag bit 255 (FROM) or 254 (TO)\n  .toB: boolean                 →       flag bit 253\n  .commissionType: \"okx\"        →       flag bit 248 (LABEL_OKX)\n```\n\n## 3. User Stories\n\n### US-1: Build Calldata (Primary)\n\n```\nAs a Solver Developer,\nI want to convert /solve API data into Settlement.settle() calldata,\nso that I can submit a settlement transaction on-chain.\n```\n\n**Scenarios**:\n\n```\nScenario: Basic calldata construction\n  Given I have a SolveRequest and SolveResponse from the /solve API\n  When I call buildSettleCalldata(request, response)\n  Then I receive a hex-encoded calldata string (0x-prefixed)\n  And I receive decoded params for inspection\n\nScenario: With DEX swap interactions\n  Given I have API data and a DEX swap route\n  When I call buildSettleCalldata(request, response, { interactions: [[], swapCalls, []] })\n  Then the calldata includes interaction-aware token indexing\n  And trade token indices are offset by tradeTokens.length\n\nScenario: Using API clearing prices\n  Given the solver API returns vetted clearing prices\n  When I call buildSettleCalldata(request, response, { useComputedPrices: false })\n  Then clearing prices are converted from decimal strings directly\n```\n\n### US-2: Decode Calldata\n\n```\nAs a Protocol Auditor,\nI want to decode hex calldata into human-readable settlement parameters,\nso that I can verify the correctness of submitted transactions.\n```\n\n**Scenarios**:\n\n```\nScenario: Level 1 - Raw ABI decode\n  Given I have a hex calldata string\n  When I call decodeSettleCalldata(calldata)\n  Then I receive settleId, tokens[], clearingPrices[], trades[], interactions[], surplusFeeInfo\n  And all numeric fields are native bigint\n\nScenario: Level 2 - Full reconstruction\n  Given I have a hex calldata string\n  When I call reconstructFromCalldata(calldata)\n  Then I receive the original SolveRequest and SolveResponse objects\n  And commission flags are unpacked to feeDirection, toB, commissionType\n  And executedAmounts are recovered from clearing prices + fee computation\n```\n\n### US-3: Verify Calldata (Round-Trip)\n\n```\nAs an Integration Engineer,\nI want to verify calldata via round-trip encode-decode-re-encode,\nso that I can confirm the encoding is correct before submitting on-chain.\n```\n\n**Scenarios**:\n\n```\nScenario: Successful round-trip\n  Given I have calldata produced by buildSettleCalldata()\n  When I reconstruct and re-encode it\n  Then the original and re-encoded calldata are byte-identical\n\nScenario: Mismatch detection\n  Given calldata has a field-level discrepancy\n  When I run field-level comparison\n  Then I receive a report listing exactly which fields differ\n```\n\n### US-4: Type-Safe Development\n\n```\nAs a Solver Developer,\nI want comprehensive TypeScript type definitions,\nso that I can catch type errors at compile time.\n```\n\n### US-5: Guided Onboarding\n\n```\nAs a new Solver Developer,\nI want Claude Code skills to guide me through the SDK,\nso that I can get productive within hours, not weeks.\n```\n\n## 4. Functional Requirements\n\n### 4.1 Calldata Encoding (Must)\n\n| ID | Requirement | Priority |\n|----|------------|----------|\n| FR-01 | `buildSettleCalldata(request, response, options?)` 接受 SolveRequest + SolveResponse 返回 hex calldata | Must |\n| FR-02 | 自动收集唯一 token 地址并构建 tokens[] 数组 | Must |\n| FR-03 | 支持两种 clearing price 模式：computed（默认）和 API 直传 | Must |\n| FR-04 | 将 API decimal string 金额转为 bigint | Must |\n| FR-05 | 打包 commission flag（direction + toB + label）为 uint256 位掩码 | Must |\n| FR-06 | 按 toTokenAddressIndex 升序排列 trades（合约要求） | Must |\n| FR-07 | 当 receiver == owner 时编码为 address(0)（gas 优化） | Must |\n| FR-08 | 支持 3 阶段 interactions [pre, swap, post]，默认为 [[], [], []] | Must |\n| FR-09 | 有 interactions 时使用 token 双倍模式（interaction tracking + trade prices） | Must |\n| FR-10 | 返回 calldata（hex）+ params（结构化参数）供检查 | Must |\n\n### 4.2 Calldata Decoding (Must)\n\n| ID | Requirement | Priority |\n|----|------------|----------|\n| FR-11 | `decodeSettleCalldata(calldata)` ABI 解码为 SDK 链上类型 | Must |\n| FR-12 | `reconstructFromCalldata(calldata)` 恢复为 API 级别类型 | Must |\n| FR-13 | `unpackCommissionFlag(flag)` 解包佣金标志位 | Must |\n| FR-14 | `unpackSolverFeeFlag(flag)` 解包 solver 费用方向 | Must |\n| FR-15 | 从 clearing prices + fee computation 恢复 executedAmounts | Must |\n| FR-16 | 恢复 receiver（address(0) → owner） | Must |\n\n### 4.3 Type System (Must)\n\n| ID | Requirement | Priority |\n|----|------------|----------|\n| FR-17 | 导出 API 格式类型：SolveRequest, SolveResponse, ApiCommissionInfo 等 | Must |\n| FR-18 | 导出链上格式类型：Trade, CommissionInfo, SolverFeeInfo, Interaction 等 | Must |\n| FR-19 | 导出常量：COMMISSION_DENOM, CommissionFlags, SIGNING_SCHEME_MAP 等 | Must |\n| FR-20 | 导出工具函数：encodeTradeFlags, decodeTradeFlags, validateOrder 等 | Must |\n\n### 4.4 Converter Utilities (Should)\n\n| ID | Requirement | Priority |\n|----|------------|----------|\n| FR-21 | `packCommissionFlag()` API fields → packed flag | Should |\n| FR-22 | `convertClearingPrices()` decimal string → uint256（最大小数位缩放） | Should |\n| FR-23 | `computeCustomPrices()` 从执行数据 + 费用计算 clearing prices | Should |\n| FR-24 | `collectTokenAddresses()` / `buildTokenIndexMap()` token 索引工具 | Should |\n| FR-25 | `buildTradeFromSolveOrders()` 合并 request + response 为 Trade | Should |\n\n### 4.5 Developer Experience (Should)\n\n| ID | Requirement | Priority |\n|----|------------|----------|\n| FR-26 | 提供 Node.js + ethers v5 完整示例项目 | Should |\n| FR-27 | 提供 Claude Code Skills（build / decode / verify） | Should |\n| FR-28 | 提供 CLAUDE.md 开发者指南（架构、构建命令、约定） | Should |\n\n## 5. Information Architecture\n\n### 5.1 Package Dependency Graph\n\n```\n@okx-intent-swap/sdk-solver   ← 用户主入口\n  ├── @okx-intent-swap/sdk-contracts  (ABI)\n  │     └── @okx-intent-swap/sdk-common\n  └── @okx-intent-swap/sdk-common     (types + utils)\n```\n\n### 5.2 Data State Machine\n\n```\n[API Data]\n    │ buildSettleCalldata()\n    ▼\n[Hex Calldata] ──── submit tx ────→ [On-Chain Settlement]\n    │\n    ├── decodeSettleCalldata()\n    ▼\n[On-Chain Types (Trade, bigint flags)]\n    │\n    ├── reconstructFromCalldata()\n    ▼\n[API Types (SolveRequest, SolveResponse)]\n    │\n    ├── buildSettleCalldata() (re-encode)\n    ▼\n[Hex Calldata'] ── compare ──→ [Match / Mismatch Report]\n```\n\n### 5.3 Fee Direction Decision Tree\n\n```\nCommissionInfos + SolverFeeInfo\n    │\n    ├── All feeDirection=true  → fromToken fees\n    │     P_s = eB,  P_b = eS - totalFromFee\n    │\n    ├── All feeDirection=false → toToken fees\n    │     toGross = eB * DENOM / (DENOM - totalPct)\n    │     P_s = toGross,  P_b = eS\n    │\n    ├── Mixed directions       → treated as fromToken\n    │\n    └── No fees (all percent=0) → P_s = eB,  P_b = eS\n```\n\n## 6. Non-Functional Requirements\n\n| Category | Requirement | Target |\n|----------|------------|--------|\n| **Performance** | 单次 buildSettleCalldata 耗时 | \u003c 5ms (10 orders) |\n| **Bundle Size** | 发布包体积（不含 ethers） | \u003c 100KB |\n| **Dependencies** | 运行时依赖数量 | 0（ethers 为 peer dep） |\n| **Compatibility** | Node.js 版本 | ≥ 18 |\n| **Compatibility** | ethers 版本 | ^5.7.0 |\n| **Compatibility** | TypeScript 版本 | ≥ 5.3 |\n| **Module Format** | ESM + CJS 双模式 | ESM primary, CJS via Jest config |\n| **Type Safety** | TypeScript strict mode | Enabled |\n| **Test Coverage** | 核心函数覆盖率 | \u003e 90% |\n\n## 7. Scope Boundaries\n\n### In Scope\n\n- Calldata 编码 / 解码 / 验证\n- API 类型 ↔ 链上类型转换\n- Flag 打包 / 解包\n- Clearing price 计算（两种模式）\n- 合约 ABI 导出\n- 示例项目和文档\n\n### Out of Scope\n\n- Solver 竞价算法\n- 链上交易提交（SDK 只生成 calldata）\n- 签名生成与验证\n- Gas 估算与优化\n- 多链支持\n- 订单持久化 / 数据库\n- 前端 UI 组件\n\n## 8. Acceptance Criteria\n\n### Feature: Calldata Encoding\n\n```\nAC-1: Given valid SolveRequest + SolveResponse, When buildSettleCalldata() is called, Then returns non-empty hex string starting with \"0x\"\nAC-2: Given multiple orders, When encoded, Then trades are sorted by toTokenAddressIndex ascending\nAC-3: Given receiver == owner, When encoded, Then trade.receiver is address(0)\nAC-4: Given interactions provided, When encoded, Then tokens[] uses double-copy pattern and indices are offset\nAC-5: Given useComputedPrices=true, When encoded, Then clearing prices are derived from execution amounts + fees\n```\n\n### Feature: Calldata Decoding\n\n```\nAC-6: Given valid calldata, When decodeSettleCalldata() is called, Then all fields are native bigint/number (no BigNumber)\nAC-7: Given valid calldata, When reconstructFromCalldata() is called, Then SolveRequest + SolveResponse match original (within documented limitations)\nAC-8: Given packed commission flag, When unpackCommissionFlag() is called, Then feeDirection, toB, commissionType are correctly extracted\n```\n\n### Feature: Round-Trip Verification\n\n```\nAC-9: Given calldata produced by buildSettleCalldata(useComputedPrices=true), When reconstructed and re-encoded, Then original == re-encoded (byte-identical)\n```\n\n## 9. Dependencies \u0026 Assumptions\n\n### External Dependencies\n\n| Dependency | Type | Risk |\n|-----------|------|------|\n| Settlement 合约 ABI | 必须同步 | ABI 变更需 SDK 发版 |\n| `/solve` API 规范 | 类型定义依据 | 格式变更需更新 types.ts |\n| ethers v5 | Peer dependency | v6 迁移需 major version bump |\n\n### Assumptions\n\n- `/solve` API 返回的 order 数组与 request 严格平行（同索引对应）\n- 费用计算使用整数除法（floor），与 Solidity 行为一致\n- COMMISSION_DENOM = 1e9 精度不变\n- EIP-712 domain (name=\"OKX Intent Swap\", version=\"v1.0.0\") 不变\n\n## 10. Open Questions\n\n| # | Question | Owner | Status | Decision |\n|---|----------|-------|--------|----------|\n| 1 | ethers v6 适配是否作为 v2.0 目标？ | SDK Team | Open | - |\n| 2 | 是否需要支持 batch auction（多 solution）？ | Protocol Team | Open | 当前仅 solutionIndex=0 |\n| 3 | 是否需要提供 Python/Go SDK？ | Product | Open | 当前仅 TypeScript |\n| 4 | npm 发布策略（public vs scoped private）？ | DevOps | Open | - |\n",
