              "content": "# Spec: OKX Intent Swap SDK\n\n\u003e Technical Specification — How do we build it?\n\n**Related**: [BRD](./brd.md) | [PRD](./prd.md) | [Plan](./plan.md)\n\n## 1. Overview\n\n- **System**: `@okx-intent-swap/sdk-*` TypeScript monorepo\n- **Summary**: 3-package SDK，通过 ABI 编码将 Solver API 数据转换为 Settlement.settle() calldata，并提供反向解码和 round-trip 验证\n- **Key Decision**: 采用 pnpm workspace + Turbo monorepo，3 包分层架构（common → contracts → solver），ethers v5 作为 ABI 编解码引擎\n\n## 2. Core Concepts\n\n### 2.1 PRD Concept → Technical Entity\n\n| PRD Concept | Technical Entity | Storage |\n|-------------|-----------------|---------|\n| SolveRequest | `SolveRequest` interface | solver/types.ts |\n| Trade | `Trade` interface | common/types.ts |\n| CommissionInfo flag | `uint256` packed bitmask | Bit positions: 255(FROM), 254(TO), 253(TOB), 248-246(LABEL) |\n| ClearingPrice | `bigint[]` parallel to `tokens[]` | Computed or converted from decimal strings |\n| Interaction | `{ target, value, callData }` tuple | 3-phase array: [pre, swap, post] |\n\n### 2.2 Invariants\n\n- `trades[]` **必须**按 `toTokenAddressIndex` 升序排列（Settlement 合约硬要求）\n- `tokens[]` 中地址不重复，保持插入顺序\n- `clearingPrices.length === tokens.length`\n- `COMMISSION_DENOM = 1_000_000_000n`（1e9），所有 feePercent 基于此精度\n- `feePercent` 总和 ≤ `COMMISSION_MAX_TOTAL_PERCENT`（30_000_000 = 3%）\n- `receiver === owner` 时编码为 `address(0)`（链上 gas 优化）\n- 费用计算使用 `floor`（整数除法），与 Solidity `mulDiv` 行为一致\n\n## 3. Architecture\n\n### 3.1 Package Dependency Diagram\n\n```\n┌──────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│  @okx-intent-swap/sdk-solver             │  ← User-facing entry point\n│  ┌─────────────┐  ┌──────────────────┐   │\n│  │ calldata-   │  │ calldata-        │   │\n│  │ builder.ts  │  │ decoder.ts       │   │\n│  │ (encode)    │  │ (decode+recon)   │   │\n│  └──────┬──────┘  └────────┬─────────┘   │\n│         │                  │             │\n│  ┌──────┴──────┐  ┌───────┴──────────┐   │\n│  │converters.ts│  │ constants.ts     │   │\n│  │(API→chain)  │  │ (flags, schemes) │   │\n│  └─────────────┘  └─────────────────┘   │\n│         │                  │             │\n│  ┌──────┴──────────────────┴──────────┐   │\n│  │           types.ts                 │   │\n│  │  (SolveRequest, SolveResponse,     │   │\n│  │   ApiCommissionInfo, ...)          │   │\n│  └────────────────────────────────────┘   │\n└──────────────┬────────────┬──────────────┘\n               │            │\n┌──────────────┴──┐  ┌──────┴──────────────┐\n│ sdk-contracts   │  │ sdk-common          │\n│ ┌─────────────┐ │  │ ┌────────────────┐  │\n│ │SETTLEMENT_  │ │  │ │ types.ts       │  │\n│ │ABI (JSON)   │ │  │ │ (Trade, Order, │  │\n│ │ERC20_ABI    │ │  │ │  CommissionInfo)│  │\n│ └─────────────┘ │  │ ├────────────────┤  │\n│                 │  │ │ constants.ts   │  │\n│                 │  │ │ (DENOM, FLAGS) │  │\n│                 │  │ ├────────────────┤  │\n│                 │  │ │ utils.ts       │  │\n│                 │  │ │ (encode/decode │  │\n│                 │  │ │  flags, validate│  │\n│                 │  │ └────────────────┘  │\n└─────────────────┘  └────────────────────┘\n```\n\n### 3.2 Module Responsibilities\n\n| Module | Responsibility | Inputs | Outputs |\n|--------|---------------|--------|---------|\n| `calldata-builder.ts` | Encode API data → hex calldata | SolveRequest, SolveResponse, Options | `{ calldata, params }` |\n| `calldata-builder.ts` (decode) | Decode hex calldata → SDK types | hex string | DecodeSettleCalldataResult |\n| `calldata-decoder.ts` | Reconstruct API types from calldata | hex string | `{ request, response, interactions }` |\n| `converters.ts` | API → on-chain type conversions | API types | Chain types (bigint, packed flags) |\n| `types.ts` (solver) | API wire format type definitions | - | TypeScript interfaces |\n| `types.ts` (common) | On-chain struct type definitions | - | TypeScript interfaces |\n| `constants.ts` (common) | Protocol constants \u0026 flag bits | - | bigint constants |\n| `utils.ts` (common) | Flag encoding, validation, helpers | Various | Various |\n\n### 3.3 Key Design Decisions\n\n| Decision | Chosen | Alternatives | Rationale |\n|----------|--------|-------------|-----------|\n| ABI library | ethers v5 | viem, ethers v6, web3.js | v5 生态最广泛，Solver 团队大概率已使用 |\n| Monorepo tool | pnpm + Turbo | yarn, lerna, nx | pnpm workspace 零配置，Turbo 缓存高效 |\n| Module format | ESM (NodeNext) | CommonJS, dual | 现代标准，`.js` 扩展名强制显式导入 |\n| Clearing price default | useComputedPrices=true | false | 从执行数据计算更确定性，匹配合约费用逻辑 |\n| Numeric type | bigint | ethers.BigNumber | 原生类型，零依赖，未来兼容 ethers v6 |\n| Test framework | Jest + ts-jest | vitest, mocha | 成熟稳定，社区支持广泛 |\n\n## 4. Data Model\n\n### 4.1 API Wire Format (solver/types.ts)\n\n```\nSolveRequest\n  auctionId: string                    -- auction identifier (decimal string)\n  orders: SolveRequestOrder[]          -- user orders\n\nSolveRequestOrder\n  fromTokenAddress: string             -- ERC20 address\n  toTokenAddress: string               -- ERC20 address\n  owner: string                        -- order signer address\n  receiver: string                     -- trade proceeds recipient\n  fromTokenAmount: string              -- decimal string (wei)\n  toTokenAmount: string                -- decimal string (wei, minimum)\n  validTo: number                      -- unix timestamp (seconds)\n  appDataHash: string                  -- bytes32 hex\n  swapMode: string                     -- \"exactIn\" | \"exactOut\"\n  partiallyFillable: boolean\n  signingScheme: string                -- \"eip712\" | \"ethSign\" | \"eip1271\" | \"preSign\"\n  signature: string                    -- hex\n  commissionInfos: ApiCommissionInfo[]\n\nApiCommissionInfo\n  feePercent: string                   -- 1e9 precision decimal string\n  referrerWalletAddress: string        -- fee recipient\n  feeDirection: boolean                -- true=fromToken, false=toToken\n  toB: boolean                         -- true=Settlement pays, false=user pays\n  commissionType: string               -- \"okx\" | \"parent\" | \"child\"\n\nSolveResponse\n  solutions: Solution[]\n\nSolution\n  clearingPrices: Record\u003cstring, string\u003e  -- lowercase address → decimal string\n  orders: SolveResponseOrder[]            -- parallel to request.orders\n  surplusFeeInfo: ApiSurplusFeeInfo\n```\n\n### 4.2 On-Chain Format (common/types.ts)\n\n```\nTrade\n  fromTokenAddressIndex: number        -- index into tokens[]\n  toTokenAddressIndex: number          -- index into tokens[]\n  owner: string                        -- address\n  receiver: string                     -- address(0) if same as owner\n  fromTokenAmount: bigint              -- uint256\n  toTokenAmount: bigint                -- uint256\n  validTo: number                      -- uint32\n  appData: string                      -- bytes32\n  flags: bigint                        -- packed: swapMode|partiallyFillable|signingScheme\n  executedAmount: bigint               -- exactIn→fromAmount, exactOut→toAmount\n  commissionInfos: CommissionInfo[]\n  signature: string                    -- hex bytes\n  solverFeeInfo: SolverFeeInfo\n\nCommissionInfo\n  feePercent: bigint                   -- uint256, 1e9 precision\n  referrerWalletAddress: string        -- address\n  flag: bigint                         -- uint256, packed bitmask\n```\n\n### 4.3 Flag Bit Layout\n\n#### CommissionInfo.flag (uint256)\n\n```\nBit 255: FROM_TOKEN_COMMISSION    (1n \u003c\u003c 255n)   feeDirection=true\nBit 254: TO_TOKEN_COMMISSION      (1n \u003c\u003c 254n)   feeDirection=false\nBit 253: IS_TO_B                  (1n \u003c\u003c 253n)   toB=true\nBit 248: LABEL_OKX                (1n \u003c\u003c 248n)   commissionType=\"okx\"\nBit 247: LABEL_PARENT             (1n \u003c\u003c 247n)   commissionType=\"parent\"\nBit 246: LABEL_CHILD              (1n \u003c\u003c 246n)   commissionType=\"child\"\nBits 0-245: reserved (0)\n```\n\n#### Trade.flags (uint256)\n\n```\nBit 0:   reserved (exactIn=0)\nBit 1:   partiallyFillable (1=partial, 0=fill-or-kill)\nBits 5-6: signingScheme (0=eip712, 1=ethSign, 2=eip1271, 3=preSign)\nBits 2-4, 7+: reserved (0)\n```\n\n#### SolverFeeInfo.flag (uint256)\n\n```\nBit 255: FROM_TOKEN   (1n \u003c\u003c 255n)   feeDirection=true\nBit 254: TO_TOKEN     (1n \u003c\u003c 254n)   feeDirection=false\n```\n\n### 4.4 Validation Rules\n\n| Field | Constraint | Error |\n|-------|-----------|-------|\n| `auctionId` | Non-empty, parseable as BigInt | \"Invalid auctionId\" |\n| `request.orders.length` | == `solution.orders.length` | \"Order count mismatch\" |\n| `fromTokenAddress` | Valid address, present in tokens[] | \"fromToken not found in tokens array\" |\n| `feePercent` | 0 ≤ value ≤ COMMISSION_MAX_TOTAL_PERCENT (cumulative) | Contract enforcement |\n| `signingScheme` | One of eip712/ethSign/eip1271/preSign | Map lookup returns undefined |\n| `solutions` | Non-empty array | \"Response contains no solutions\" |\n\n## 5. API / Interface Design\n\n### 5.1 Primary API: buildSettleCalldata\n\n```typescript\nfunction buildSettleCalldata(\n  request: SolveRequest,\n  response: SolveResponse,\n  options?: BuildSettleCalldataOptions\n): BuildSettleCalldataResult\n\ninterface BuildSettleCalldataOptions {\n  interactions?: [Interaction[], Interaction[], Interaction[]]  // default: [[], [], []]\n  solutionIndex?: number                                        // default: 0\n  useComputedPrices?: boolean                                   // default: true\n}\n\ninterface BuildSettleCalldataResult {\n  calldata: string       // 0x-prefixed hex\n  params: {\n    settleId: bigint\n    tokens: string[]\n    clearingPrices: bigint[]\n    trades: Trade[]\n    interactions: [Interaction[], Interaction[], Interaction[]]\n    surplusFeeInfo: SurplusFeeInfo\n  }\n}\n```\n\n### 5.2 Decode API: decodeSettleCalldata\n\n```typescript\nfunction decodeSettleCalldata(calldata: string): DecodeSettleCalldataResult\n\ninterface DecodeSettleCalldataResult {\n  settleId: bigint\n  tokens: string[]              // checksummed addresses\n  clearingPrices: bigint[]\n  trades: Trade[]\n  interactions: [Interaction[], Interaction[], Interaction[]]\n  surplusFeeInfo: SurplusFeeInfo\n}\n```\n\n### 5.3 Reconstruct API: reconstructFromCalldata\n\n```typescript\nfunction reconstructFromCalldata(calldata: string): ReconstructFromCalldataResult\n\ninterface ReconstructFromCalldataResult {\n  request: SolveRequest\n  response: SolveResponse\n  interactions: [Interaction[], Interaction[], Interaction[]]\n}\n```\n\n### 5.4 Utility APIs\n\n```typescript\n// Flag packing/unpacking\nfunction packCommissionFlag(feeDirection: boolean, toB: boolean, commissionType: string): bigint\nfunction unpackCommissionFlag(flag: bigint): { feeDirection: boolean; toB: boolean; commissionType: string }\nfunction unpackSolverFeeFlag(flag: bigint): boolean  // returns feeDirection\n\n// Trade flags\nfunction encodeTradeFlags(swapMode: OrderKind, partiallyFillable: boolean, signingScheme: number): bigint\nfunction decodeTradeFlags(flags: bigint): { swapMode: OrderKind; partiallyFillable: boolean; signingScheme: number }\n\n// Price computation\nfunction computeCustomPrices(eS: bigint, eB: bigint, commissionInfos: ApiCommissionInfo[], solverFeeInfo: ApiSolverFeeInfo): CustomPriceResult\nfunction convertClearingPrices(apiPrices: ClearingPrices, tokenAddresses: string[]): bigint[]\n```\n\n## 6. Clearing Price Computation\n\n### 6.1 Computed Mode (default, useComputedPrices=true)\n\nPer-order custom price computation from execution amounts + fees:\n\n**Case 1: fromToken fees (or no fees)**\n\n```\ntotalFromFee = Σ floor(eS × feePercent_i / DENOM)  +  floor(eS × solverFeePercent / DENOM)\nP_s = eB                           (clearingPrices[fromTokenIndex])\nP_b = eS - totalFromFee            (clearingPrices[toTokenIndex])\n```\n\n**Case 2: toToken fees**\n\n```\ntotalPct = Σ feePercent_i + solverFeePercent\ntoGross = ceil(eB × DENOM / (DENOM - totalPct))     // iterative adjustment\nP_s = toGross                      (clearingPrices[fromTokenIndex])\nP_b = eS                           (clearingPrices[toTokenIndex])\n```\n\n**Case 3: No fees**\n\n```\nP_s = eB\nP_b = eS\n```\n\n### 6.2 API Mode (useComputedPrices=false)\n\n```\n1. Collect all decimal prices from solution.clearingPrices\n2. Find maxDecimals across all price strings\n3. Scale all prices × 10^maxDecimals → bigint[]\n4. Align to tokens[] order\n```\n\n### 6.3 Interaction Token Offset\n\nWhen interactions are present:\n\n```\ntokens = [...tradeTokens, ...tradeTokens]\n         ↑ interaction tracking (price=0)  ↑ trade prices (actual)\n\ntradeTokenIndexMap: address → index + tradeTokens.length\nclearingPrices = [0n...0n, tradePrices...]\n```\n\n## 7. Security\n\n### 7.1 SDK Security Boundary\n\nSDK **不负责**：\n- 签名验证（合约层 EIP-712/eth_sign 验证）\n- 订单过期检查（合约层 `validTo` 检查）\n- 余额/授权检查（合约层 token transfer 检查）\n- 费率上限执行（合约层 `COMMISSION_MAX_TOTAL_PERCENT` 检查）\n\nSDK **负责**：\n- 类型安全（TypeScript strict mode）\n- 输入验证（order count mismatch, missing tokens, empty solutions）\n- 正确的 ABI 编码（匹配合约 settle() 签名）\n\n### 7.2 Sensitivity Protection\n\n- 无硬编码地址或私钥\n- 示例数据使用虚拟地址（`0x1234...`）\n- 合约 ABI 为公开信息（Foundry 编译输出）\n\n## 8. Build \u0026 CI\n\n### 8.1 Build Pipeline\n\n```\npnpm install → Turbo: build(common) → build(contracts) → build(solver) → build(example)\n                                ↓ dependsOn                ↓ dependsOn\n```\n\n### 8.2 Test Pipeline\n\n```\npnpm test → Turbo: test(all) → Jest(ts-jest) → CommonJS transform → Run tests\n```\n\n### 8.3 Module Convention\n\n| Rule | Detail |\n|------|--------|\n| Package type | `\"type\": \"module\"` (ESM) |\n| tsconfig module | `NodeNext` |\n| Relative imports | **Must include `.js` extension** |\n| JSON imports | Require `with { type: 'json' }` |\n| Jest override | `tsconfig.jest.json` → CommonJS |\n| Module mapping | `@okx-intent-swap/*` → source dirs |\n\n## 9. Testing Strategy\n\n| Level | Target | Method | Coverage |\n|-------|--------|--------|----------|\n| Unit | Flag packing/unpacking | Jest assertions | All flag combinations |\n| Unit | Type converters | Jest + fixture data | All API→chain conversions |\n| Unit | Price computation | Jest + edge cases | fromToken/toToken/no fees × exactIn/exactOut |\n| Integration | buildSettleCalldata | End-to-end with decode | Full encode-decode round-trip |\n| Integration | reconstructFromCalldata | Round-trip re-encode | Byte-identical comparison |\n| E2E | Example project | Build + run | Compilable, executable |\n\n**Test Files**:\n\n```\npackages/common/src/__tests__/utils.test.ts          (utilities)\npackages/solver/src/__tests__/calldata-builder.test.ts (44 cases)\npackages/solver/src/__tests__/build-calldata-e2e.test.ts (E2E)\n```\n\n## 10. Distribution\n\n### 10.1 npm Package Structure\n\n```\n@okx-intent-swap/sdk-solver/\n  dist/\n    index.js          (ESM)\n    index.d.ts        (declarations)\n    calldata-builder.js\n    calldata-decoder.js\n    converters.js\n    types.js\n    constants.js\n  package.json\n    main: \"dist/index.js\"\n    types: \"dist/index.d.ts\"\n    files: [\"dist\"]\n    peerDependencies: { ethers: \"^5.7.0\" }\n```\n\n### 10.2 Installation\n\n```bash\npnpm add @okx-intent-swap/sdk-solver ethers@^5.7.0\n# sdk-common and sdk-contracts are transitive dependencies\n```\n",
