              "content": "# Plan: OKX Intent Swap SDK\n\n\u003e Implementation Plan — When and in what order do we build it?\n\n**Related**: [BRD](./brd.md) | [PRD](./prd.md) | [Spec](./spec.md)\n\n## 1. Overview\n\n- **Project**: OKX Intent Swap SDK v1.0\n- **Summary**: 4 阶段交付，从仓库初始化到文档齐全的可发布 SDK\n- **Total Phases**: 4\n- **Current Status**: Phase 1-4 全部完成（仓库已处于 production-ready 状态）\n\n```\nPhase 1: Foundation     → 仓库骨架 + 基础类型\nPhase 2: Core Encoding  → buildSettleCalldata() 完整实现\nPhase 3: Decode \u0026 Verify → 反向解码 + round-trip 验证\nPhase 4: DX \u0026 Publish   → 文档、示例、Skills、发布准备\n```\n\n---\n\n## Phase 1: Foundation\n\n**Goal**: 建立 monorepo 骨架，定义核心类型系统和常量。\n\n**Deliverables**:\n- [x] pnpm workspace + Turbo 配置\n- [x] `@okx-intent-swap/sdk-common` 包（types + constants + utils）\n- [x] `@okx-intent-swap/sdk-contracts` 包（ABI JSON）\n- [x] `@okx-intent-swap/sdk-solver` 包骨架（types.ts）\n- [x] TypeScript 配置（strict mode, ESM, path aliases）\n- [x] Jest 测试框架（ts-jest, moduleNameMapper）\n- [x] MIT LICENSE\n\n**Tasks**:\n\n| # | Task | Depends On | Verification |\n|---|------|-----------|-------------|\n| 1.1 | 初始化 Git 仓库 + .gitignore | - | `git status` clean |\n| 1.2 | 配置 pnpm workspace + Turbo | 1.1 | `pnpm install` 成功 |\n| 1.3 | 创建 sdk-common: types.ts (Trade, Order, CommissionInfo, Interaction, SurplusFeeInfo) | 1.2 | `pnpm typecheck` 通过 |\n| 1.4 | 创建 sdk-common: constants.ts (COMMISSION_DENOM, CommissionFlags, LABEL_*, EIP712_DOMAIN) | 1.2 | 常量可导入 |\n| 1.5 | 创建 sdk-common: utils.ts (encodeTradeFlags, decodeTradeFlags, validateOrder, hex/bytes utils) | 1.3, 1.4 | `pnpm test` utils.test.ts 通过 |\n| 1.6 | 创建 sdk-contracts: Settlement ABI + ERC20 ABI (Foundry JSON) | 1.2 | ABI 可导入，Interface 可实例化 |\n| 1.7 | 创建 sdk-solver: types.ts (SolveRequest, SolveResponse, ApiCommissionInfo, ApiSolverFeeInfo) | 1.3 | TypeScript 编译通过 |\n| 1.8 | 创建 sdk-solver: constants.ts (SIGNING_SCHEME_MAP, SolverFeeFlags, ADDRESS_ZERO) | 1.4 | 常量可导入 |\n| 1.9 | 配置 Jest + ts-jest + tsconfig.jest.json (CommonJ